  "prompt": "What are some alternatives to yelp in India?",
  "response": "In India, several alternatives to Yelp provide reviews and listings of local businesses, including restaurants and services. Some popular options include:\n\n1. **Zomato**: Originally started in India, Zomato is a prominent platform for restaurant discovery, food delivery, and reviews.\n\n2. **Swiggy**: Known primarily as a food delivery service, Swiggy also has a feature called Swiggy Genie and Swiggy Go, which offer customer reviews and ratings for restaurants.\n\n3. **Magicpin**: It is a local discovery platform that helps users discover dining, fashion, beauty, and grocery options, offering cashback and deals.\n\n4. **TripAdvisor**: Internationally known for travel-related content and reviews, TripAdvisor is widely used in India for restaurant and hotel reviews.\n\n5. **Google Maps**: Many people use Google Maps for finding local businesses and reading reviews, as it is an integrated tool that combines navigation with business information.\n\n6. **Justdial**: This is a comprehensive local search service in India which provides reviews, ratings, and contact information for a wide range of businesses.\n\n7. **Nearbuy**: Offers discovery and deals on various services like restaurants, spas, salons, and more, helping users find local businesses and experiences.\n\nThese platforms provide a variety of tools and features for users to rate, review, and discover local businesses across different categories.",
